    // FAQs - Overview
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsAcquisition.q': 'What is the Acquisition module?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsAcquisition.a': 'The Acquisition module helps you manage the entire sales pipeline from lead capture to contract signing. It includes leads management, proposal requests, quotes, proposals, and contracts.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.modulesIncluded.q': 'What modules are included?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.modulesIncluded.a': '• Leads - Capture and qualify potential clients\n• Deals (Proposal Requests) - Track sales opportunities\n• Quotes - Build detailed pricing quotes\n• Proposals - Create professional proposals\n• Contracts - Manage signed agreements',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.howToStart.q': 'How do I get started?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.howToStart.a': 'Start by capturing leads through campaigns or manual entry. Qualify leads and convert them to deals. Create quotes and proposals, then close with a contract.',

    // FAQs - Leads
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsLead.q': 'What is a Lead?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsLead.a': 'A lead is a potential client who has shown interest in your products or services. Leads can come from marketing campaigns, website forms, referrals, or manual entry.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.leadStatuses.q': 'What are the lead statuses?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.leadStatuses.a': '• New - Recently captured, not yet contacted\n• Contacted - Initial contact made\n• No Answer - Could not reach\n• Callback Scheduled - Follow-up planned\n• Visit Scheduled - Meeting arranged\n• Qualified - Ready for proposal\n• Converted - Became a client\n• Lost - Did not convert',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.leadToClient.q': 'How do I convert a lead to a client?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.leadToClient.a': 'When a lead is qualified and ready, you can link them to a Deal (proposal request). Once the deal is won, the lead becomes a client in your contacts.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.leadWorkflows.q': 'Can I automate lead workflows?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.leadWorkflows.a': 'Yes! In the Leads page, go to the Workflow tab to configure automatic status changes, notifications, and actions based on lead events.',

    // FAQs - Deals
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsDeal.q': 'What is a Deal (Proposal Request)?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsDeal.a': 'A Deal represents a sales opportunity. It tracks the potential value, probability of closing, and current stage of the negotiation.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.dealStages.q': 'What are the deal stages?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.dealStages.a': '• Lead - Initial stage\n• Contact - In discussion\n• Proposal - Quote/proposal sent\n• Negotiation - Terms being discussed\n• Won - Deal closed successfully\n• Lost - Did not close',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.dealToQuote.q': 'How do I create a quote from a deal?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.dealToQuote.a': 'Open the deal and click "Create Quote" or go to Quotes and select the deal when creating a new quote. The quote will be linked to that deal.',

    // FAQs - Quotes
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsQuote.q': 'What is a Quote?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsQuote.a': 'A quote is a detailed pricing document that lists products, services, quantities, and prices. It calculates totals, discounts, and taxes automatically.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.quoteTemplates.q': 'Can I use templates for quotes?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.quoteTemplates.a': 'Yes! Create quote templates with pre-defined items, discounts, and settings. When creating a new quote, select a template to start with those items.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.quoteToProposal.q': 'How do I convert a quote to a proposal?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.quoteToProposal.a': 'In the quote page, click "Generate Proposal" to create a professional proposal document based on the quote items and totals.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.quotePricing.q': 'How does pricing work?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.quotePricing.a': 'Each item has a unit price, quantity, and optional discount. The system calculates:\n• Subtotal = Price × Quantity\n• Line Discount applied\n• Global Discount applied\n• Service Fees added\n• VAT/Tax calculated\n• Grand Total computed',

    // FAQs - Proposals
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsProposal.q': 'What is a Proposal?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsProposal.a': 'A proposal is a professional document sent to clients. It includes your branding, the quote details, terms and conditions, and can be customized with rich text.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.proposalCustomization.q': 'Can I customize proposal appearance?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.proposalCustomization.a': 'Yes! Use proposal templates to define the layout, colors, logo, header, footer, and sections. Each company can have its own branded templates.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.proposalSending.q': 'How do I send a proposal?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.proposalSending.a': 'Click "Send Proposal" to email it directly to the client. They receive a link to view and accept the proposal online.',

    // FAQs - Contracts
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsContract.q': 'What is a Contract?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.whatIsContract.a': 'A contract is a formal agreement with the client. It documents the services/products agreed upon, pricing, terms, and is signed by both parties.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.contractSignature.q': 'How does contract signing work?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.contractSignature.a': 'Contracts can be signed digitally. The client receives a link to view and sign. Once signed, both parties receive a copy of the signed document.',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.contractTemplates.q': 'Can I use contract templates?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.contractTemplates.a': 'Yes! Create contract templates with standard clauses, terms, and formatting. Select a template when creating a new contract.',

    // FAQs - Workflows
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.salesWorkflow.q': 'What is the typical sales workflow?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.salesWorkflow.a': '1. Lead is captured (campaign, form, manual)\n2. Lead is qualified (contacted, scored)\n3. Deal is created for qualified leads\n4. Quote is built with items and pricing\n5. Proposal is generated and sent\n6. Contract is signed when accepted\n7. Lead converts to client',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.automations.q': 'What automations are available?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.automations.a': '• Automatic lead status changes\n• Email notifications on stage changes\n• Callback and visit reminders\n• AI-powered scheduling suggestions\n• Workflow triggers for custom actions',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.customWorkflows.q': 'Can I customize the workflow?',
    'acquisitionHelp.faq.customWorkflows.a': 'Yes! Each company can configure their own workflow stages, status names, and automation rules. Go to Leads > Workflow to customize.',

